resources.string: In order to add a Komponent open Kustom and press + on the editor ToolBar, then select Komponent and find this pack
In order to use this preset you will need Kustom installed with PRO license unless this is a featured free theme
App has been hidden from launcher and will not show up on the drawer from next restart, you can off course still access it from Kustom. If you want the app back on your Launcher please reinstall it.
